metadata.name: Mercedes-Benz #1
metadata.description: The Mercedes AMG GT NFT is the epitome of digital luxury, an exclusive and unparalleled masterpiece that captures the essence of the Mercedes AMG GT sports car. This remarkable FT is a one-of-a-kind collectible, designed to satisfy the most sophisticated of tastes and the most discerning of collectors. Every detail of this artwork has been crafted with the utmost precision, from the elegant curves and lines of the AMG GT to the unparalleled attention to detail that characterizes the Mercedes brand.
